snippet.textDisplay: Adnan’s lyrics are simple yet so impactful. The instrumental arrangements are also quite sophisticated. This kalam sounds different with open speakers and headfones. With headfones you can listen to many subtle instruments that are hard to listen to in open speaker. I was worried if someone will match Rohail’s pace, but it appears xulfi is on the right track. Great start mate, onwards and upwards!!
